print("Virat Kohli, an Indian cricketer, holds the record for being the fastest player to score 8,000, 9,000, 10,000, 11,000, and 12,000 runs in One Day International (ODI) cricket. He achieved each milestone in fewer innings than any other player in the history of the game. Kohli's incredible consistency and remarkable batting skills have earned him numerous accolades and established him as one of the greatest cricketers of his generation.")
